{"name": "faicons", "metadata": {"name": "faicons", "version": "0.2.2", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 2 - Pre-Alpha", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9", "Topic :: Text Processing :: Markup :: HTML"], "home_page": "https://github.com/rstudio/py-faicons", "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["htmltools"], "summary": "An interface to Font-Awesome for use in Shiny.", "upload_time": 1705447639}, "documentation": ["\n# Font Awesome for Shiny\n\nAn interface to [Font-Awesome](https://fontawesome.com/) for use in Shiny for Python.\n\nThis package currently uses Font-Awesome 6.2.0.\n\n## Installation\n\n```python\npip install faicons\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nUse `icon_svg()` to get an `<svg>` representation of the icon.\n\n```python\nfrom faicons import icon_svg\nicon_svg(\"play\")\n```\n\nExample usage in Shiny:\n\n```python\nfrom shiny import ui\nui.input_action_button(\"btn\", \"Press me\", icon=icon_svg(\"play\")).show()\n```\n\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "faicons._core", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "faicons._core.metadata", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Get the metadata for all icons.\n\nReturns:\n  A dictionary of icon metadata.\n\nExamples:"]}, {"name": "faicons._core.icon_svg", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "name", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "style", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "fill", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "fill_opacity", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "stroke", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "stroke_width", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "stroke_opacity", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "height", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "width", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "margin_left", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "margin_right", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "position", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "title", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "a11y", "type": {"name": "Literal", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Literal", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "\"deco\"", "xref": null, "params": null}, {"name": "\"sem\"", "xref": null, "params": null}, {"name": "\"none\"", "xref": null, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "Tag", "xref": {"fqname": "htmltools.Tag", "project": "htmltools"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Generate Font Awesome icons as SVGs\n\nParameters:\n  name: The icon's name (e.g., \"play\", \"pause\", etc).\n\n  style: The FontAwesome style for the icon (e.g., \"regular\", \"solid\", etc).\n\n  fill: The icon's fill color.\n\n  fill_opacity: The icon's fill opacity (0.0 - 1.0).\n\n  stroke: The icon's stroke color.\n\n  stroke_width: The icon's stroke width.\n\n  stroke_opacity: The icon's stroke opacity (0.0 - 1.0).\n\n  height: The icon's height.\n\n  width: The icon's width.\n\n  margin_left: The icon's left margin.\n\n  margin_right: The icon's right margin.\n\n  position: The icon's position (e.g., \"absolute\", \"relative\", etc).\n\n  title: A description of the icon to display on mouse hover.\n  When `a11y == \"sem\"`, this description is also used as an aria-label\n  (otherwise, the icon's inherent label is used for the aria-label).\n\n  a11y: Either \"deco\" (decorative) or \"sem\" (semantic). Using \"none\" will\n  result in no accessibility features for the icon.\n\nReturns:\n  An HTML string containing the SVG of the icon.\n\nRaises:\n  ValueError: If the icon name is not valid."]}, {"name": "faicons._core._parse_length_unit", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "x", "type": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Optional", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Optional", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "ParsedUnit", "xref": {"fqname": "faicons._core.ParsedUnit", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "faicons._core._ICONS", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "faicons._core._css_length_units", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "faicons._core.IconDataSvg", "bases": ["TypedDict"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "faicons._core.IconDataSvg.last_modified", "type": {"name": "float", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.float", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "faicons._core.IconDataSvg.raw", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "faicons._core.IconDataSvg.viewBox", "type": {"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "faicons._core.IconDataSvg.width", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "faicons._core.IconDataSvg.height", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "faicons._core.IconDataSvg.path", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_cla